1
00:01:25,510 --> 00:01:29,880
[Coroner's Diary]

2
00:01:30,900 --> 00:01:33,920
[Episode 28]

3
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:49,229
Little Wan'er,

4
00:01:49,250 --> 00:01:51,009
that was a close one.

5
00:01:51,039 --> 00:01:54,039
Yan Li told me
Minister Li is very high-maintenance.

6
00:01:54,350 --> 00:01:56,580
If he files a complaint against you
to the Emperor,

7
00:01:56,580 --> 00:01:58,950
you'll lose access to
the Ministry of Justice.

8
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:01,030
We'd better stay away from him.

9
00:02:01,759 --> 00:02:03,560
I should've been more cautious.

10
00:02:03,759 --> 00:02:06,650
I must not drag you and Yan Li
into danger again.

11
00:02:07,090 --> 00:02:07,870
I

12
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:09,950
used to be a loner.

13
00:02:10,070 --> 00:02:11,730
I wasn't considerate enough.

14
00:02:12,030 --> 00:02:12,950
From now on,

15
00:02:12,970 --> 00:02:14,670
I can't put you guys at risk again.

16
00:02:14,670 --> 00:02:16,620
It's not as serious as you imagine.

17
00:02:17,370 --> 00:02:18,449
Besides,

18
00:02:18,560 --> 00:02:20,550
I'm glad to go through trouble with you.

19
00:02:20,550 --> 00:02:21,950
But it upsets me.

20
00:02:22,560 --> 00:02:23,420
Little Wan'er,

21
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:26,410
ever since the day I met you,

22
00:02:27,450 --> 00:02:29,910
I've always known
you're no ordinary woman.

23
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,490
I only hope

24
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:34,440
that you won't be held back by anything

25
00:02:34,720 --> 00:02:36,920
and that you'll always stride forward.

26
00:02:37,040 --> 00:02:39,660
If you're constrained
by the fear of implicating me,

27
00:02:39,660 --> 00:02:41,660
that will truly break my heart.

28
00:02:47,370 --> 00:02:49,360
I can't believe I just said those words.

29
00:02:49,360 --> 00:02:51,360
What a rare and precious friend I am.

30
00:02:57,810 --> 00:02:58,410
Ning,

31
00:02:59,000 --> 00:02:59,760
in fact...

32
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:01,810
I'm not Qin Wan.

33
00:03:02,210 --> 00:03:03,579
I am Shen Yi's daughter,

34
00:03:03,880 --> 00:03:04,690
Shen Wan.

35
00:03:12,040 --> 00:03:12,650
You...

36
00:03:13,720 --> 00:03:14,790
Does Chi...

37
00:03:15,210 --> 00:03:16,370
He knew it long ago.

38
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:18,960
You...

39
00:03:19,070 --> 00:03:20,690
I'm concealing my real identity

40
00:03:20,690 --> 00:03:23,220
for the purpose of
clearing my father's name.

41
00:03:24,090 --> 00:03:25,270
Are you crazy?

42
00:03:25,480 --> 00:03:27,210
How could you just blurt it out?

43
00:03:27,280 --> 00:03:28,880
You treat me with sincerity,

44
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:31,450
so I don't want to deceive you anymore.

45
00:03:32,250 --> 00:03:33,410
That doesn't mean

46
00:03:33,410 --> 00:03:35,740
I'd like to know such an important secret.

47
00:03:36,370 --> 00:03:38,170
Keeping secrets is exhausting.

48
00:03:38,280 --> 00:03:39,040
Besides,

49
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:41,780
why should I care about your surname?

50
00:03:42,130 --> 00:03:43,460
Can a different surname

51
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:45,310
change who you really are?

52
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:47,720
I'm still me.

53
00:03:48,360 --> 00:03:50,290
I'm the same girl you met on day one.

54
00:03:51,320 --> 00:03:52,720
That's all I need to know.

55
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:54,430
I'll pretend

56
00:03:54,750 --> 00:03:56,320
not to have heard any of that.

57
00:03:56,320 --> 00:03:57,410
From now on,

58
00:03:57,410 --> 00:03:59,370
we'll behave the exact same way as before.

59
00:03:59,370 --> 00:04:00,170
Since Shen...

60
00:04:01,570 --> 00:04:03,829
your father was an upstanding official,

61
00:04:03,880 --> 00:04:06,340
I won't blame you
for telling me this secret.

62
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,720
Then,

63
00:04:10,970 --> 00:04:11,970
Yan Li...

64
00:04:13,200 --> 00:04:14,600
Don't tell him the truth.

65
00:04:14,810 --> 00:04:15,690
What if he gets drunk someday

66
00:04:15,690 --> 00:04:17,220
and has a slip of the tongue?

67
00:04:18,130 --> 00:04:18,850
Well,

68
00:04:19,130 --> 00:04:20,990
I'll let you in on another secret.

69
00:04:21,420 --> 00:04:22,250
Actually...

70
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:23,850
I'm older than you!

71
00:04:27,089 --> 00:04:28,920
Little Wan'er!

72
00:04:28,920 --> 00:04:30,029
You...

73
00:04:30,209 --> 00:04:32,540
You kept me in the dark
for the entire time!

74
00:04:32,570 --> 00:04:34,010
How could do you do that?

75
00:04:39,680 --> 00:04:40,720
The Ministry of War

76
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,570
plans to to shift the blame

77
00:04:41,570 --> 00:04:43,330
to those transport commissioners.

78
00:04:43,330 --> 00:04:44,720
Prince Cheng supervises
the Ministry of War.

79
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,180
This is probably his idea.

80
00:04:47,120 --> 00:04:48,320
Tell the Dove Unit now

81
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:50,360
to find out who in the Shuoxi Army is

82
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,220
in contact with

83
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,760
the Transport Bureau of Xibei Prefecture.

84
00:04:53,890 --> 00:04:56,010
I won't let Prince Cheng
easily get away

85
00:04:56,010 --> 00:04:57,450
by sacrificing a scapegoat.

86
00:04:57,450 --> 00:04:58,710
Master, do you suspect

87
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,850
that there's a mole in the Shuoxi Army?

88
00:05:00,850 --> 00:05:01,770
If not,

89
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:04,690
how could those transport commissioners

90
00:05:04,690 --> 00:05:06,650
have possibly snuck the moldy grains

91
00:05:06,650 --> 00:05:08,409
into the Shuoxi Army's granary?

92
00:05:08,409 --> 00:05:09,159
Shall we

93
00:05:09,800 --> 00:05:11,660
inform Prince Rui of this matter?

94
00:05:15,650 --> 00:05:16,480
Father

95
00:05:16,850 --> 00:05:18,800
sees all his soldiers as family.

96
00:05:19,680 --> 00:05:20,720
If I tell him

97
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,480
that I'll conduct an investigation
inside the Shuoxi Army,

98
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,140
do you think he will believe me

99
00:05:25,160 --> 00:05:26,410
or scold me, accusing me of

100
00:05:26,410 --> 00:05:27,680
eagerly pursuing short-term interests

101
00:05:27,680 --> 00:05:29,480
and sabotaging our great cause?

102
00:05:30,010 --> 00:05:30,770
Master.

103
00:05:35,410 --> 00:05:36,010
Go.

104
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:39,250
For the Shuoxi soldiers

105
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:42,340
and the civilians in the border area,

106
00:05:43,120 --> 00:05:44,720
we must do what has to be done.

107
00:05:45,010 --> 00:05:45,650
Yes.

108
00:05:48,210 --> 00:05:50,570
Hu Dequan was responsible for
harvesting and producing ice.

109
00:05:50,570 --> 00:05:51,500
He usually lived

110
00:05:51,650 --> 00:05:54,120
in the backyard to watch the ice cellar
for the restaurant.

111
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,180
Who would've known

112
00:05:55,570 --> 00:05:57,700
he'd freeze to death in the ice cellar?

113
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:59,409
Did anyone touch anything here?

114
00:05:59,409 --> 00:05:59,970
No.

115
00:06:00,409 --> 00:06:02,240
The owner of Zuixian Restaurant
reported to the prefect's office

116
00:06:02,240 --> 00:06:03,480
right after he discovered the victim.

117
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,240
Nobody had come in here before we arrived.

118
00:06:05,240 --> 00:06:06,680
When you reached this place,

119
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:09,159
was the first door of the ice cellar
already open?

120
00:06:09,159 --> 00:06:09,720
Yes.

121
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:27,630
Take an impression of this footprint now.

122
00:06:37,090 --> 00:06:38,040
Could it be...

123
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:40,640
the victim's footprint?

124
00:06:40,720 --> 00:06:41,410
No.

125
00:06:41,850 --> 00:06:43,360
Judging from the victim's clothes

126
00:06:43,360 --> 00:06:45,360
and the soil at the back of his shoes,

127
00:06:45,409 --> 00:06:47,920
the killer must've dragged
the victim's body into here

128
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,450
after killing him outside.

129
00:06:49,480 --> 00:06:51,720
By then, the first door had been
open for a while.

130
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,970
Some ice around had melted into water.

131
00:06:54,280 --> 00:06:56,720
So, the soil attached to the bottoms of
the murderer's shoes turned into mud,

132
00:06:56,720 --> 00:06:58,720
leaving footprints all along the way.

133
00:06:58,720 --> 00:07:01,240
But since he grabbed the victim
from behind as he walked in,

134
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:03,490
his footprints were wiped away
by the victim's body.

135
00:07:03,490 --> 00:07:04,800
When the murderer got to this spot,

136
00:07:04,800 --> 00:07:07,650
the mud on the bottoms of his shoes
was almost all gone.

137
00:07:07,650 --> 00:07:09,310
After he laid the victim down,

138
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,800
for some reason,

139
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:13,130
the victim's body exactly
covered the one last footprint,

140
00:07:13,130 --> 00:07:15,040
but he didn't realize it.

141
00:07:15,120 --> 00:07:17,530
Then, the murderer took his shoes off

142
00:07:17,530 --> 00:07:19,390
and left the ice cellar barefoot.

143
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:31,320
I just won't tell you.

144
00:07:31,810 --> 00:07:33,070
Little Wan'er carries

145
00:07:33,070 --> 00:07:34,870
the legacy of ancestral wisdom.

146
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,530
The ice punishment...

147
00:07:50,010 --> 00:07:51,210
The killings were indeed arranged

148
00:07:51,210 --> 00:07:52,650
according to the Seven-Layered Inferno.

149
00:07:52,650 --> 00:07:53,510
Your Highness,

150
00:07:53,900 --> 00:07:54,700
the problem is

151
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:57,900
the Black Unrighteous Flower
is nowhere to be seen.

152
00:08:12,450 --> 00:08:13,650
Close the door now.

153
00:08:13,650 --> 00:08:14,510
Close the door!

154
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:02,520
The ice punishment

155
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:03,480
is designed for

156
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,340
those who betray their families.

157
00:09:05,930 --> 00:09:07,450
Who on earth did this?

158
00:09:07,880 --> 00:09:08,580
Ning,

159
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:09,760
go with Yan Li to find out

160
00:09:09,760 --> 00:09:11,690
if the victim got along with
his family and friends.

161
00:09:11,690 --> 00:09:12,240
Got it!

162
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:19,530
What exactly is going on between them?

163
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:21,690
Wait up!

164
00:09:22,720 --> 00:09:23,520
Sir,

165
00:09:24,170 --> 00:09:26,850
someone died in the ice cellar
of your restaurant.

166
00:09:26,850 --> 00:09:28,930
I'm afraid your business will be affected.

167
00:09:28,930 --> 00:09:30,660
That's what I'm worried about.

168
00:09:30,970 --> 00:09:32,120
When Hu Dequan was alive,

169
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,720
he was already a menace.

170
00:09:33,720 --> 00:09:35,480
Now, even his death is causing me trouble.

171
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,540
If I had known this,

172
00:09:36,970 --> 00:09:39,430
I wouldn't have kindly
taken him in at first.

173
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,290
It sounds like

174
00:09:41,290 --> 00:09:43,620
Hu Dequan wasn't
much of a nice guy, was he?

175
00:09:44,330 --> 00:09:46,850
He used to work as a purchaser
for the restaurant.

176
00:09:46,850 --> 00:09:48,690
His gambling addiction

177
00:09:48,690 --> 00:09:50,090
got him into heavy debts.

178
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:52,980
Then, he sold his only daughter
to a brothel.

179
00:09:53,290 --> 00:09:55,550
But instead of learning a lesson from it,

180
00:09:55,850 --> 00:09:58,030
he gambled again and lost all that money.

181
00:09:58,030 --> 00:10:00,210
What's worse, the banker broke his legs.

182
00:10:00,210 --> 00:10:03,170
He could barely make a living,
so he turned to me for help.

183
00:10:03,170 --> 00:10:04,400
Out of pity,

184
00:10:04,400 --> 00:10:06,200
I let him stay in the back quarters

185
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,860
to look after the ice cellar
for the restaurant.

186
00:10:10,680 --> 00:10:11,710
Sir, do you know

187
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:13,190
which brothel

188
00:10:13,210 --> 00:10:15,210
Hu Dequan sold his daughter to?

189
00:10:15,660 --> 00:10:16,780
I think it was...

190
00:10:17,210 --> 00:10:18,450
Fengqi House.

191
00:10:34,000 --> 00:10:35,260
Don't, Your Highness!

192
00:10:36,780 --> 00:10:37,510
It's okay.

193
00:10:37,760 --> 00:10:39,820
This powder is burned Datura leaves.

194
00:10:39,850 --> 00:10:41,520
It's available at any pharmacy.

195
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,850
Datura leaves?

196
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,850
Does Your Highness mean

197
00:10:45,050 --> 00:10:47,000
the murderer drugged the victim first

198
00:10:47,000 --> 00:10:48,480
before dragging him into the ice cellar

199
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:50,280
and letting him freeze to death?

200
00:10:51,210 --> 00:10:53,720
The smile on the victim's face
is the best proof.

201
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,290
Before a man freezes to death,

202
00:10:55,290 --> 00:10:57,210
the blood in him
would start circulating slowly.

203
00:10:57,210 --> 00:10:59,050
Delightful hallucinations are
likely to occur

204
00:10:59,050 --> 00:11:01,050
to relieve the man of physical pain.

205
00:11:01,210 --> 00:11:03,050
That's why smiles tend to
appear on the faces

206
00:11:03,050 --> 00:11:04,580
of those freezing to death.

207
00:11:04,970 --> 00:11:06,480
There are only undergarments
on the victim.

208
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:09,450
It suggests that he was going to bed
when he was drugged.

209
00:11:09,450 --> 00:11:10,480
In his abode,

210
00:11:10,690 --> 00:11:13,420
there should be residue of
burned Datura leaves.

211
00:11:13,600 --> 00:11:14,170
Got it.

212
00:11:35,570 --> 00:11:38,230
The Datura powder was
placed in the candle wick.

213
00:11:38,850 --> 00:11:39,710
Little Wan'er.

214
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,170
We found

215
00:11:43,170 --> 00:11:45,400
where Hu Dequan sold his daughter to—

216
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,450
Fengqi House.

217
00:11:47,050 --> 00:11:48,850
The first victim also visited

218
00:11:48,850 --> 00:11:49,760
Fengqi House.

219
00:11:49,830 --> 00:11:51,830
The second victim, Zhao Jiaxu,

220
00:11:51,860 --> 00:11:53,690
had a mistress from Fengqi House.

221
00:11:53,690 --> 00:11:55,210
The third victim was
connected to Fengqi House too.

222
00:11:55,210 --> 00:11:56,340
This is our finding.

223
00:11:57,810 --> 00:11:58,520
The link

224
00:11:58,520 --> 00:12:01,180
among these victims
has finally been revealed.

225
00:12:07,760 --> 00:12:09,170
What's the matter, Little Wan'er?

226
00:12:09,170 --> 00:12:11,230
Did you catch a cold in the ice cellar?

227
00:12:11,290 --> 00:12:12,950
I'm usually better than that.

228
00:12:13,210 --> 00:12:16,340
But I've been working cases non-stop
during these days.

229
00:12:18,000 --> 00:12:19,530
Greetings, Your Highness.

230
00:12:20,810 --> 00:12:21,450
Chi.

231
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,360
Chi.

232
00:12:34,090 --> 00:12:35,120
What are you doing?

233
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,360
It was just a few coughs.

234
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:37,210
Put me down.

235
00:12:37,820 --> 00:12:38,750
Don't act tough.

236
00:12:41,930 --> 00:12:43,190
Everyone, attention!

237
00:12:43,810 --> 00:12:44,740
Close your eyes!

238
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:45,690
Turn around!

239
00:12:46,670 --> 00:12:48,070
Do you know when

240
00:12:48,120 --> 00:12:49,090
to avert your eyes?

241
00:12:49,090 --> 00:12:49,810
Yes!

242
00:12:49,810 --> 00:12:51,110
Do you know what

243
00:12:51,330 --> 00:12:52,210
not to say?

244
00:12:52,210 --> 00:12:53,000
Yes!

245
00:13:02,360 --> 00:13:03,810
Young man,

246
00:13:03,810 --> 00:13:05,930
well done. A bright future awaits you.

247
00:13:05,930 --> 00:13:07,130
Thank Your Highness.

248
00:13:07,180 --> 00:13:08,210
I was only doing my job.

249
00:13:08,210 --> 00:13:09,000
Very good.

250
00:13:12,090 --> 00:13:13,420
What are you looking at?

251
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,480
What's wrong?

252
00:13:15,880 --> 00:13:17,290
Your eyes fixed on him,

253
00:13:17,520 --> 00:13:19,780
like a hungry wolf staring at a fat sheep.

254
00:13:20,050 --> 00:13:21,570
That's not true!

255
00:13:22,970 --> 00:13:23,900
Close your eyes.

256
00:13:24,210 --> 00:13:24,940
Turn around.

257
00:13:27,870 --> 00:13:29,770
Do you know when

258
00:13:30,090 --> 00:13:31,150
to avert your eyes?

259
00:13:44,170 --> 00:13:44,640
Come on.

260
00:13:53,340 --> 00:13:54,170
I prepared

261
00:13:54,170 --> 00:13:56,570
this medicine for you
in the Herbal Garden.

262
00:13:57,260 --> 00:13:57,910
I tried it.

263
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,330
It cures a cold fast.

264
00:14:06,090 --> 00:14:06,820
Here you are.

265
00:14:20,760 --> 00:14:22,520
How's the military provision case going?

266
00:14:22,520 --> 00:14:24,090
I've found out everything they let out.

267
00:14:24,090 --> 00:14:25,290
As for what they don't want to let out,

268
00:14:25,290 --> 00:14:27,360
I'll have it revealed sooner or later.

269
00:14:27,360 --> 00:14:28,530
Just don't worry.

270
00:14:30,400 --> 00:14:33,930
I told Ning about my real identity.

271
00:14:35,210 --> 00:14:36,000
I see.

272
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:38,040
Get some sleep now.

273
00:14:38,170 --> 00:14:39,520
You'll feel better after sweating a bit.

274
00:14:39,520 --> 00:14:40,120
Come here.

275
00:14:53,300 --> 00:14:57,060
[Qin Residence]

276
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,480
My Lady, you finally woke up.

277
00:15:12,480 --> 00:15:13,810
Are you feeling better?

278
00:15:17,400 --> 00:15:18,360
Come with me now.

279
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:19,820
People have been waiting.

280
00:15:37,820 --> 00:15:38,980
Just like Yingqi,

281
00:15:39,410 --> 00:15:40,980
