318
00:17:12,050 --> 00:17:15,670
I heard the ice punishment
had appeared today.

319
00:17:15,770 --> 00:17:17,490
I'd better get back to my room

320
00:17:17,490 --> 00:17:20,119
to ponder over the cases in Guanyin Town.

321
00:17:21,200 --> 00:17:23,599
That way, a certain someone will stop

322
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:27,119
calling me a mercenary fraud.

323
00:17:49,680 --> 00:17:50,530
Don't be afraid.

324
00:17:50,530 --> 00:17:51,260
I'm here.

325
00:17:59,490 --> 00:18:00,880
Ning,

326
