360
00:19:26,400 --> 00:19:28,120
Those who know Hu Dequan,

361
00:19:29,000 --> 00:19:29,960
step forward.

362
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:41,880
The rest of you may leave.

363
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:42,920
You three stay.

364
00:19:47,490 --> 00:19:48,440
Let's figure out

365
00:19:48,440 --> 00:19:49,490
who else

366
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:52,350
has asked you about these three people.

367
