Confiscated properties can be resold.

375
00:21:00,600 --> 00:21:02,290
Lord Shen was an honest officer.

376
00:21:02,290 --> 00:21:04,120
This old house is in a remote location.

377
00:21:04,120 --> 00:21:05,810
Nobles have no interest in it.

378
00:21:06,770 --> 00:21:08,370
Plus, it is related to a case.

379
00:21:08,530 --> 00:21:09,960
So, I was able to buy it

380
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:11,900
in the name of a brokerage.

381
00:21:14,290 --> 00:21:15,490
