383
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:22,260
I'm just happy to get back what I lost.

384
00:21:22,730 --> 00:21:23,640
I'm not upset.

385
00:21:29,900 --> 00:21:32,470
I dreamed about this tree on the carriage.

386
00:21:33,770 --> 00:21:34,770
When I was little,

387
00:21:35,400 --> 00:21:37,400
when I didn't want to do needlework,

388
00:21:37,530 --> 00:21:39,050
I'd climb up this tree.

389
00:21:39,680 --> 00:21:41,400
My mother, furiously holding a ruler,

390
00:21:41,400 --> 00:21:43,330
would stomp her feet on the ground.

391
00:21:48,850 --> 00:21:50,730
Being punished by a loving mother

392
00:21:52,600 --> 00:21:54,730
is actually a thing to be grateful for.

393
00:21:58,160 --> 00:22:00,160
If Princess Consort Rui were alive,

394
00:22:00,440 --> 00:22:02,700
I'm sure she would be just like my mother.

395
00:22:02,920 --> 00:22:03,920
She would love you

396
00:22:04,570 --> 00:22:06,600
and cherish you with all her heart.

397
00:22:07,440 --> 00:22:08,960
If you misbehaved,

398
00:22:09,330 --> 00:22:11,360
