399
00:22:23,260 --> 00:22:24,520
Today, I read the files

400
00:22:26,140 --> 00:22:28,770
about my father and Prince Jin
in the Court of Judicial Review.

401
00:22:28,770 --> 00:22:29,810
I know what crimes

402
00:22:29,810 --> 00:22:31,680
they fabricated against my father,

403
00:22:31,680 --> 00:22:33,610
and how they slandered Prince Jin.

404
00:22:34,680 --> 00:22:36,920
This is a battle we must win

405
00:22:37,200 --> 00:22:38,680
at all costs.

406
00:22:39,730 --> 00:22:40,640
Did you notice

407
00:22:40,640 --> 00:22:42,240
anything odd in those files?

408
