when he was drunk.

411
00:22:49,280 --> 00:22:50,810
But that was not a real confession.

412
00:22:50,810 --> 00:22:52,440
Prince Jin's silence
during the interrogation

413
00:22:52,440 --> 00:22:53,300
was recorded as

414
00:22:53,510 --> 00:22:55,240
"unable to provide an answer."

415
00:22:55,640 --> 00:22:56,700
The files also say,

416
00:22:57,090 --> 00:22:58,670
Prince Jin was standing beside

417
00:22:58,670 --> 00:23:00,400
Consort Jin's body
with a dagger in his hand.

418
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:02,900
How could someone drunk enough
to commit those heinous crimes

419
00:23:02,900 --> 00:23:04,920
have possibly stood steadily on his feet?

420
00:23:04,920 --> 00:23:06,720
Then in the file about Lord Shen,

421
00:23:06,850 --> 00:23:08,850
did you notice anything suspicious?

422
00:23:08,850 --> 00:23:10,050
The file says

423
00:23:11,090 --> 00:23:13,160
my father hid some physical evidence
of Prince Jin's case.

424
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:13,810
But it doesn't

425
00:23:13,810 --> 00:23:15,600
specify any items.

426
00:23:16,250 --> 00:23:17,450
Just like Prince Jin,

427
00:23:18,330 --> 00:23:19,920
my father confessed to his crimes

428
00:23:19,920 --> 00:23:21,860
by being "unable to provide an answer."

429
00:23:21,860 --> 00:23:22,900
Li Muyun must've

430
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,650
tampered with those two files.

431
00:23:24,770 --> 00:23:25,520
My father and Prince Jin

432
00:23:25,520 --> 00:23:27,380
would never commit those crimes.

433
00:23:27,850 --> 00:23:30,250
I'm worried this might be
a trap set up by Li Muyun.

434
00:23:30,250 --> 00:23:31,200
If he discovers

435
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:34,010
you've read Lord Shen's
and Prince Jin's files,

436
00:23:34,010 --> 00:23:35,670
and reports it to the Emperor,

437
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:36,640
I'm afraid

438
00:23:37,090 --> 00:23:39,220
we'll have to flee and never come back.

439
00:23:39,960 --> 00:23:41,820
I shouldn't have acted so rashly.

440
00:23:43,600 --> 00:23:45,810
Would Li Muyun go to such great lengths

441
00:23:46,060 --> 00:23:47,450
only to test us?

442
00:23:48,340 --> 00:23:49,470
I'm afraid he also wants to identify

443
00:23:49,470 --> 00:23:51,600
those attempting to
reopen Prince Jin's case

444
00:23:51,600 --> 00:23:52,930
and eliminate them all.

445
00:23:53,640 --> 00:23:55,090
Then I'll stay low for a while

446
00:23:55,090 --> 00:23:56,360
to avoid alerting him.

447
00:23:58,250 --> 00:23:58,960
Be patient.

448
00:23:59,400 --> 00:24:01,930
We're getting closer and closer
to the truth.

449
00:24:07,050 --> 00:24:07,920
Are you okay?

450
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:09,360
It hurts.

451
00:24:09,450 --> 00:24:10,600
I'm in pain.

452
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:11,730
I didn't know it'd break...

453
00:24:11,730 --> 00:24:13,560
Stop talking. It's all your fault.

454
00:24:13,560 --> 00:24:14,490
My bottom hurts terribly.

455
00:24:14,490 --> 00:24:15,200
Put me down now.

456
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,200
Okay, okay.

457
00:24:22,470 --> 00:24:23,950
Master, Your Highness.

458
00:24:24,530 --> 00:24:26,060
What are you two doing here?

459
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:29,960
Well...

460
00:24:29,960 --> 00:24:30,810
You say it.

