465
00:24:39,530 --> 00:24:40,660
It broke in the end.

466
00:24:42,570 --> 00:24:43,770
Two people, huh?

467
00:24:45,010 --> 00:24:46,060
Your Highness!

468
00:24:47,090 --> 00:24:49,160
Why did you have to be so explicit?

469
00:24:59,010 --> 00:24:59,490
Wan,

470
00:25:00,090 --> 00:25:01,090
