00:25:07,770 --> 00:25:09,100
Don't worry about me...

476
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:10,090
and Fuling.

477
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,360
Good for you.

478
00:25:17,640 --> 00:25:19,770
