485
00:25:32,490 --> 00:25:33,620
What does that mean?

486
00:25:34,640 --> 00:25:37,200
Did Princess Yongci
say something to you, Master?

487
00:25:37,200 --> 00:25:38,730
Please don't be mad, Master.

488
00:25:38,730 --> 00:25:39,990
If I come up with a good idea again,

489
00:25:39,990 --> 00:25:41,920
I promise I'll tell you right away!

490
00:25:45,290 --> 00:25:46,400
Let me get through.

491
00:25:48,010 --> 00:25:49,740
I told you to let me get through!

492
00:25:54,100 --> 00:25:55,670
Let go of me. I'm Zhang Dongxuan.

493
00:25:55,670 --> 00:25:58,400
I have something urgent
to tell Princess Yongci!

494
00:25:58,610 --> 00:26:02,340
Nobody can enter the inner quarters
without Master's permission.

495
00:26:02,730 --> 00:26:03,670
Release him.

496
00:26:13,090 --> 00:26:13,770
Your Highness,

497
00:26:13,770 --> 00:26:15,330
where did you recruit these people from?

498
00:26:15,330 --> 00:26:16,960
They assaulted me
without knowing who I am.

499
00:26:16,960 --> 00:26:17,850
If I had been hurt,

500
00:26:17,850 --> 00:26:20,140
let's see how you're going to
explain to Princess Yongci!

501
00:26:20,140 --> 00:26:21,060
Cut the crap.

502
00:26:21,600 --> 00:26:23,600
Why do you want to meet the princess?

503
00:26:34,810 --> 00:26:37,680
I figured out a pattern by studying

504
00:26:37,680 --> 00:26:39,850
the three murders in Guanyin Town.

505
00:26:40,770 --> 00:26:42,500
You're better than I expected.

506
00:26:42,570 --> 00:26:43,800
A man's life will be endangered.

507
00:26:43,800 --> 00:26:46,310
Now is not the time to taunt me,
Your Highness.

508
00:26:46,310 --> 00:26:47,370
My calculation results

509
00:26:47,370 --> 00:26:50,430
indicate that the fourth killing
will happen tonight.

510
00:26:50,880 --> 00:26:52,480
The fourth killing tonight?

511
00:26:52,770 --> 00:26:54,430
One more than in Guanyin Town?

512
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,850
Yes.

513
00:26:58,140 --> 00:27:00,930
My deductions were made
based on the calendar and the regular way

514
00:27:00,930 --> 00:27:02,850
that the leader
of the Heavenly Way Society acts.

515
00:27:02,850 --> 00:27:04,640
But I can't guarantee the accuracy

516
00:27:04,640 --> 00:27:06,010
of these results.

517
00:27:06,290 --> 00:27:08,250
Following the key principles
of the calendar,

518
00:27:08,250 --> 00:27:09,640
I deduced seven dates.

519
00:27:09,640 --> 00:27:11,250
Tonight, it'll be time

520
00:27:13,960 --> 00:27:15,360
for the fire punishment.

521
00:27:15,530 --> 00:27:16,730
If Your Highness is convinced,

522
00:27:16,730 --> 00:27:17,810
please get prepared soon.

523
00:27:17,810 --> 00:27:18,600
But if not,

524
00:27:18,600 --> 00:27:20,200
then forget what I just said.

525
00:27:24,110 --> 00:27:24,700
Now,

526
00:27:25,530 --> 00:27:27,680
it is not confirmed
if a murder will happen,

527
00:27:27,680 --> 00:27:29,480
or where and when it will happen.

528
00:27:29,640 --> 00:27:31,010
We must patrol
throughout the night,

529
00:27:31,010 --> 00:27:32,960
so as to discover any fires
as early as possible.

530
00:27:32,960 --> 00:27:33,960
If a fire happens,

531
00:27:34,780 --> 00:27:35,780
save lives first!

532
00:27:35,990 --> 00:27:36,640
Yes!

533
00:27:41,330 --> 00:27:42,090
Set out!

534
00:27:42,090 --> 00:27:42,670
Let's go!

535
00:28:06,160 --> 00:28:07,160
It's 11 p.m. now.

536
00:28:07,800 --> 00:28:09,250
Nothing has happened yet.

537
00:28:09,250 --> 00:28:09,920
Indeed.

538
00:28:14,160 --> 00:28:15,220
What's that place?

539
00:28:16,120 --> 00:28:18,400
That's the Jade Street in the East Market.

540
00:28:18,400 --> 00:28:19,360
Sound the alarm.

541
00:28:19,420 --> 00:28:21,110
Send the fire rescue team there!

542
00:28:21,110 --> 00:28:22,040
Sound the alarm!

543
00:28:55,600 --> 00:28:56,800
How is this possible?

544
00:28:57,330 --> 00:28:58,260
It can't be true.

545
00:28:58,680 --> 00:28:59,610
It can't be true!

546
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:10,480
Wan.

547
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:18,050
Yan Chi!

548
00:29:22,800 --> 00:29:23,530
Wan.

549
00:29:31,090 --> 00:29:32,420
Did you have a bad dream?

550
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,680
