551
00:29:35,010 --> 00:29:36,050
I was terrified.

552
00:29:37,360 --> 00:29:39,820
There really is
a mental rapport between us.

553
00:29:42,860 --> 00:29:43,730
What happened?

554
00:29:44,580 --> 00:29:46,780
Someone received the fire punishment.

555
00:29:49,500 --> 00:29:51,890
