00:30:05,730 --> 00:30:07,330
That's the victim's mother.

564
00:30:08,050 --> 00:30:10,560
The murderer only spread oil
around the victim.

565
00:30:10,560 --> 00:30:13,200
That's why the fire didn't reach
farther places quickly.

566
00:30:13,200 --> 00:30:14,570
Too bad that I arrived too late.

567
00:30:14,570 --> 00:30:15,970
I wasn't able to save him.

568
00:30:23,010 --> 00:30:25,000
Mr. Wang was always meticulous.

569
00:30:25,320 --> 00:30:27,380
How did he let a fire start in his shop?

570
00:30:27,920 --> 00:30:30,160
Could it be related to the recent murders?

571
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,250
That's impossible.

572
00:30:31,250 --> 00:30:33,810
I heard the killer would only
go after bad people.

573
00:30:33,810 --> 00:30:35,290
Mr. Wang was very nice.

574
00:30:35,290 --> 00:30:37,250
How did he get in this kind of trouble?

575
00:30:37,250 --> 00:30:39,120
Maybe he had a dark side you don't know.

576
00:30:39,120 --> 00:30:39,880
Cut it out!

577
00:30:40,530 --> 00:30:41,640
Only a few of us know

578
00:30:41,640 --> 00:30:43,300
the details of these murders.

579
00:30:43,600 --> 00:30:45,530
How did these civilians get to know

580
00:30:45,640 --> 00:30:48,700
that the previous victims were
considered bad people?

581
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:51,360
Those in the Heavenly Way Society
have the details too.

582
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:53,960
I suppose they'd let out
the victims' information

583
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:56,440
before executing them
in the name of serving justice.

584
00:30:56,440 --> 00:30:57,880
If someone in the capital is

585
00:30:57,880 --> 00:30:59,530
using the Heavenly Way Society

586
00:30:59,530 --> 00:31:01,640
to eliminate opponents
and confuse the Emperor,

587
00:31:01,640 --> 00:31:02,700
then I'm afraid

588
00:31:02,850 --> 00:31:04,880
the capital will soon plunge into chaos.

589
00:31:04,880 --> 00:31:06,480
But now we're short of leads.

590
00:31:07,010 --> 00:31:09,410
God knows
when the murderer will be caught.

591
00:31:09,810 --> 00:31:10,470
Don't fret.

592
00:31:10,810 --> 00:31:12,090
That's just a speculation.

593
00:31:12,090 --> 00:31:13,930
Perhaps the situation
won't develop that way.

594
00:31:13,930 --> 00:31:15,460
All you need to do is focus on

595
00:31:15,550 --> 00:31:16,750
searching for leads.

596
00:31:16,940 --> 00:31:18,400
I'll take care of the rest.

597
00:31:18,920 --> 00:31:19,600
Okay.

598
00:31:20,210 --> 00:31:22,740
The suspect of the military provision case
is being escorted to the capital.

599
00:31:22,740 --> 00:31:23,430
During these days,

600
00:31:23,430 --> 00:31:25,640
I may have to spend more time
in the Ministry of War.

601
00:31:25,640 --> 00:31:26,850
I'll have Bai Feng follow you around.

602
00:31:26,850 --> 00:31:27,530
Don't.

603
00:31:28,050 --> 00:31:29,490
That's a rather complicated case.

604
00:31:29,490 --> 00:31:30,880
You need a helpful aide.

605
00:31:31,440 --> 00:31:33,360
Yan Li and Ning are all I need.

606
00:31:41,210 --> 00:31:42,170
Water...

607
00:31:54,940 --> 00:31:55,980
Let me have a sip.

608
00:32:03,660 --> 00:32:04,180
You...

609
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:05,040
You...

610
00:32:05,250 --> 00:32:06,140
You... you...

611
00:32:11,210 --> 00:32:12,450
What?

612
00:32:22,230 --> 00:32:23,510
What did you do to me?

613
00:32:26,560 --> 00:32:27,120
I...

614
00:32:27,290 --> 00:32:27,920
I...

615
00:32:28,600 --> 00:32:30,600
Stop disgusting me!

616
00:32:30,600 --> 00:32:31,290
I...

617
00:32:31,640 --> 00:32:33,440
What did you do to me?

618
00:32:33,770 --> 00:32:35,680
Did you deliberately get me drunk

619
00:32:35,740 --> 00:32:37,260
to take advantage of me?

620
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:38,570
My goodness.

621
00:32:38,870 --> 00:32:40,870
Who took advantage of whom exactly?

622
00:32:44,090 --> 00:32:44,810
Come on!

623
00:32:45,910 --> 00:32:47,190
Drink it up.

624
00:32:47,570 --> 00:32:50,360
From now on,

625
00:32:50,360 --> 00:32:52,570
the world will know us as

626
00:32:52,570 --> 00:32:53,520
Yong,

627
00:32:53,970 --> 00:32:54,880
Li—

628
00:32:54,960 --> 00:32:57,050
the legendary detectives.

629
00:32:57,640 --> 00:32:58,340
Cheers!

630
00:33:00,110 --> 00:33:01,630
Yong and Li?

631
00:33:02,330 --> 00:33:03,390
We should be called

632
00:33:03,440 --> 00:33:04,410
the inseparable

633
00:33:04,770 --> 00:33:05,530
duo!

634
00:33:05,900 --> 00:33:06,600
Duo?

635
00:33:07,400 --> 00:33:08,120
Okay.

636
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:10,940
Drink this up,
and we'll be the inseparable duo.

637
00:33:10,940 --> 00:33:13,340
If you don't, we'll just be Yong and Li!

638
00:33:13,570 --> 00:33:14,360
Deal!

639
00:33:14,850 --> 00:33:15,730
Bottoms up!

640
00:33:15,730 --> 00:33:16,390
Bottoms up!

641
00:33:44,600 --> 00:33:45,850
Li,

642
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:47,460
listen.

643
00:33:48,120 --> 00:33:49,570
In fact...

644
00:33:50,830 --> 00:33:52,350
except Little Wan'er,

645
00:33:52,770 --> 00:33:55,180
you're the smartest person

646
00:33:55,200 --> 00:33:56,990
in the world.

647
00:33:57,440 --> 00:33:59,770
You bet I am. I know that.

648
00:33:59,770 --> 00:34:00,980
Besides,

649
00:34:01,360 --> 00:34:03,290
I feel

650
00:34:03,490 --> 00:34:05,300
the happiest...

651
00:34:05,460 --> 00:34:07,630
when I'm with you.

652
00:34:15,120 --> 00:34:16,120
Then...

653
00:34:17,490 --> 00:34:19,040
would you consider

654
00:34:20,389 --> 00:34:21,310
marrying me?

655
00:34:31,420 --> 00:34:33,139
I'm feeling terrible.

656
00:34:33,310 --> 00:34:35,800
Pat my back now, please.

657
00:34:41,650 --> 00:34:42,659
Yong and Li?

658
00:34:43,420 --> 00:34:45,230
What an awful name.

659
00:34:45,570 --> 00:34:46,830
I must be really drunk.

660
00:34:49,130 --> 00:34:49,850
Do you

661
00:34:50,400 --> 00:34:52,400
really not remember anything?

662
00:34:54,830 --> 00:34:56,159
What should I remember?

663
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:59,659
All I can remember
is that I felt terribly dizzy yesterday.

664
00:35:01,080 --> 00:35:02,440
Just because I can't recall anything

665
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:03,610
doesn't mean you can fool me.

666
00:35:03,610 --> 00:35:05,469
I have zero tolerance for deceit!

667
00:35:07,850 --> 00:35:09,650
What can I gain from fooling you?

668
00:35:11,000 --> 00:35:12,550
Look at my face.

669
00:35:12,840 --> 00:35:13,710
I'm the one who suffered a loss.

670
00:35:13,710 --> 00:35:15,290
Stop talking nonsense!

671
00:35:17,320 --> 00:35:19,040
You just won't admit
you took advantage of me, right?

672
00:35:19,040 --> 00:35:20,610
Let's go back to the palace

673
00:35:20,610 --> 00:35:22,440
to meet the Empress Dowager
and the Grand Princess now.

674
00:35:22,440 --> 00:35:24,330
We'll tell them we slept outside
last night

675
00:35:24,330 --> 00:35:26,660
and ask them to decide
which of us is right.

676
00:35:28,690 --> 00:35:30,690
If you ever let out a word about this,

677
00:35:30,920 --> 00:35:33,520
I'll make sure
you don't have any descendants!

678
00:35:34,400 --> 00:35:36,610
If Little Wan'er asks about last night,

679
00:35:36,610 --> 00:35:37,440
just tell her

680
00:35:37,680 --> 00:35:40,410
we spent the whole night
investigating the case.

681
00:35:42,650 --> 00:35:43,740
Do you hear me?

682
00:35:45,650 --> 00:35:47,400
I do. I do.

683
00:35:48,130 --> 00:35:48,770
Plus,

684
00:35:49,730 --> 00:35:50,590
you must forget

685
00:35:50,870 --> 00:35:52,850
everything that happened last night.

686
00:35:52,850 --> 00:35:54,650
Don't ever think about it again!

687
00:35:58,130 --> 00:35:59,080
Ning,

688
00:35:59,730 --> 00:36:00,850
you're wrong.

689
00:36:01,560 --> 00:36:02,590
If I forget it,

690
00:36:03,610 --> 00:36:05,010
my mind will be all empty.

691
00:36:06,610 --> 00:36:08,610
If I'm not allowed to think about it,

692
00:36:09,810 --> 00:36:11,470
then I won't have to forget it.

693
00:36:20,260 --> 00:36:23,050
You two must've had great fun last night.

694
00:36:23,620 --> 00:36:26,230
Why not pay the bill now?

695
00:36:26,730 --> 00:36:27,320
Pay up.

696
00:36:37,040 --> 00:36:38,100
Where is the money?

697
00:37:23,580 --> 00:37:24,870
[Postmortem Report]

698
00:37:25,480 --> 00:37:26,340
Your Highness,

699
00:37:29,130 --> 00:37:30,860
here is the postmortem report.

700
00:37:32,920 --> 00:37:34,850
I have completed the examination.

701
00:37:35,290 --> 00:37:38,090
The victim's arms
wrapped around a bronze pillar.

702
00:37:38,760 --> 00:37:40,020
He was severely burned

703
00:37:40,250 --> 00:37:42,980
from the top of his head
to the bottoms of his feet.

704
00:37:43,320 --> 00:37:45,880
I'm not sure if Datura powder was used.

705
00:37:46,360 --> 00:37:47,160
That said,

706
00:37:47,330 --> 00:37:49,290
there are no signs of a struggle
on the body.

707
00:37:49,290 --> 00:37:52,040
Traces of powder were found in the lungs.

708
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:53,290
I believe

709
00:37:54,040 --> 00:37:55,040
the victim

710
00:37:55,040 --> 00:37:57,480
had become unconscious
before the fire was on.

711
00:37:57,480 --> 00:37:59,770
The victim probably
died of smoke inhalation

712
00:37:59,770 --> 00:38:00,900
and burns to organs.

713
00:38:01,250 --> 00:38:03,170
On the back of the body

714
00:38:03,250 --> 00:38:04,920
and in the bed at the crime scene,

715
00:38:04,920 --> 00:38:06,780
I found a small amount of mercury.

716
00:38:07,300 --> 00:38:09,050
That was probably left

717
00:38:09,340 --> 00:38:12,070
after the cinnabar
in the red lead chalks burned.

718
00:38:15,730 --> 00:38:16,590
Your Highness,

719
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,160
did I

720
00:38:18,540 --> 00:38:19,540
miss anything?

721
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:22,660
You conducted a through check, Mr. Fang.

722
00:38:23,080 --> 00:38:23,960
I'm flattered.

723
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:25,860
Your Highness,

724
00:38:26,850 --> 00:38:28,440
to be perfectly candid,

725
00:38:29,070 --> 00:38:31,270
despite my ten-odd years' experience,

726
00:38:32,360 --> 00:38:34,090
I remained a mediocre coroner.

727
00:38:34,340 --> 00:38:35,740
I didn't realize this job

728
00:38:36,140 --> 00:38:37,540
could save lives

729
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:40,080
and restore justice for the society

730
00:38:40,160 --> 00:38:41,760
until I met you.

731
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,250
I have no regrets anymore.

732
00:38:50,730 --> 00:38:52,260
Thank you for the hard work.

733
00:39:03,660 --> 00:39:04,810
Ouch! It hurts!

734
00:39:04,810 --> 00:39:05,770
Not so hard, Chi!

735
00:39:05,770 --> 00:39:07,040
-The two of you...
-I'll never do it again!

736
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:08,810
One is a prince's heir,
and the other a princess.

737
00:39:08,810 --> 00:39:09,880
What a disgrace to fight

738
00:39:09,880 --> 00:39:11,540
in a brothel over a small bill!

739
00:39:11,560 --> 00:39:13,820
Do you even know what humiliation means?

740
00:39:14,130 --> 00:39:15,360
Not so loud.

741
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:18,060
It'll be a bigger humiliation
if people hear us.

742
00:39:18,260 --> 00:39:19,120
What happened?

743
00:39:19,410 --> 00:39:20,610
-Nothing!
-Nothing!

744
00:39:21,960 --> 00:39:22,760
The two of them

745
00:39:25,830 --> 00:39:27,580
found a lead in Fengqi House.

746
00:39:28,360 --> 00:39:29,290
-Right!
-Right!

747
00:39:29,390 --> 00:39:30,790
Quite an important lead.

748
00:39:32,960 --> 00:39:34,080
The person who knows the three victims

749
00:39:34,080 --> 00:39:35,440
and has asked the girls

750
00:39:35,440 --> 00:39:36,970
at Fengqi House about them

751
00:39:37,230 --> 00:39:39,670
is the carver dismissed by Ranmo Gallery—

752
00:39:39,700 --> 00:39:40,900
-Wang Xin!
-Wang Xin!

753
00:39:41,470 --> 00:39:43,200
A carver doesn't get paid much.

754
00:39:43,320 --> 00:39:45,960
How can Wang Xin afford
frequent visits to Fengqi House?

755
00:39:45,960 --> 00:39:46,770
Little Wan'er,

756
00:39:46,770 --> 00:39:48,250
let me tell you something.

757
00:39:48,480 --> 00:39:50,360
Carvers go to brothels

758
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:51,770
not to spend money,

759
00:39:52,070 --> 00:39:53,800
but to make money.

760
00:39:54,330 --> 00:39:55,860
The ladies there sometimes

761
00:39:55,870 --> 00:39:59,000
coax those pretentious scholars
into gifting them

762
00:39:59,020 --> 00:40:00,290
seals, jade pendants and such.

763
00:40:00,290 --> 00:40:02,330
When the carvers get paid,

764
00:40:02,330 --> 00:40:05,360
they'll share some profits
with the girls.

765
00:40:07,250 --> 00:40:09,000
Both sides will benefit.

766
00:40:10,250 --> 00:40:13,450
You seem quite familiar with
how things work in brothels.

767
00:40:13,920 --> 00:40:15,960
There's nothing about brothels

768
00:40:16,520 --> 00:40:17,170
that I...

769
00:40:17,170 --> 00:40:18,630
can't find out with money.

770
00:40:19,290 --> 00:40:20,960
Don't even get me started on it.

771
00:40:20,960 --> 00:40:22,520
If you hadn't squandered all the money,

772
00:40:22,520 --> 00:40:25,850
would I have had to wrestle with
those people in the brothel?

773
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:30,080
Ning, Li,

774
00:40:30,080 --> 00:40:31,850
the information you got is very helpful.

775
00:40:31,850 --> 00:40:32,630
However,

776
00:40:33,080 --> 00:40:34,560
you got drunk during an investigation

777
00:40:34,560 --> 00:40:35,520
and nearly jeopardized our work.

778
00:40:35,520 --> 00:40:36,610
Merits offset faults.

779
00:40:36,610 --> 00:40:37,660
If you make one more blunder,

780
00:40:37,660 --> 00:40:39,360
I won't let you join me
in future investigations.

781
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:40,170
Understood?

782
00:40:40,500 --> 00:40:41,600
-Understood.
-Understood.

783
00:40:41,600 --> 00:40:43,320
When I'm in the Ministry of War,

784
00:40:43,320 --> 00:40:44,580
you must keep Wan safe.

785
00:40:45,010 --> 00:40:47,010
Rest assured. With me and Ning here,

786
00:40:47,040 --> 00:40:49,100
Little Wan'er will be safe and sound.

787
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,080
Don't worry.

788
00:40:53,110 --> 00:40:54,070
I'll go with them

789
00:40:54,100 --> 00:40:56,130
to visit Wang Shouchang's mother later.

790
00:40:56,130 --> 00:40:56,650
Okay.

791
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:02,740
Little Wan'er,

792
00:41:02,960 --> 00:41:05,160
how did you know we got drunk last night?

793
00:41:05,830 --> 00:41:07,100
If not,

794
00:41:07,200 --> 00:41:09,470
how could your smell have got on him?

795
00:41:15,750 --> 00:41:17,010
I didn't say anything.

796
00:41:21,400 --> 00:41:22,850
To be honest, Your Highness,

797
00:41:22,850 --> 00:41:24,960
Shouchang used to be a naughty kid.

798
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,060
At the age of eight,

799
00:41:27,560 --> 00:41:30,690
he burned down an abandoned hut
when he played with fire,

800
00:41:30,980 --> 00:41:32,070
without knowing

801
00:41:32,440 --> 00:41:35,000
an old beggar was in it,
hiding from the cold.

802
00:41:35,330 --> 00:41:36,730
He didn't realize it

803
00:41:37,040 --> 00:41:38,840
until screams reached his ears.

804
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:40,960
By then, the blaze had become too intense.

805
00:41:40,960 --> 00:41:43,010
Shouchang wanted to rescue the beggar,

806
00:41:43,010 --> 00:41:44,140
but he got cold feet.

807
00:41:44,690 --> 00:41:47,090
Then that old beggar was unfortunately...

808
00:41:48,440 --> 00:41:50,250
What a terrible accident.

809
00:41:53,880 --> 00:41:55,810
Does anyone else know about this?

810
00:41:56,520 --> 00:41:57,690
No, I guess not.

811
00:41:58,130 --> 00:42:01,040
Not a day went by
without Shouchang feeling guilty.

812
00:42:01,650 --> 00:42:03,360
He became more and more quiet.

813
00:42:04,140 --> 00:42:07,140
But he did occasionally

814
00:42:07,160 --> 00:42:09,300
chat with a jade carver named Wang Xin,

815
00:42:09,470 --> 00:42:11,070
who worked in Ranmo Gallery.

816
00:42:12,050 --> 00:42:13,850
Shouchang shouldn't have died.

817
00:42:17,560 --> 00:42:18,960
Wang Shouchang set a fire and took a life.

818
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:20,610
But that was an honest mistake.

819
00:42:20,610 --> 00:42:22,670
He was not an unscrupulous criminal.

820
00:42:23,360 --> 00:42:24,960
A man who sincerely repented on his wrongs

821
00:42:24,960 --> 00:42:26,520
was tortured and killed brutally.

822
00:42:26,520 --> 00:42:29,520
How can it be justified
as walking the "Heavenly Way"?

823
00:42:29,690 --> 00:42:32,490
The "Heavenly Way" is
defined by a man's thinking.

824
00:42:32,560 --> 00:42:34,290
If a man's thinking strays from
the right track,

825
00:42:34,290 --> 00:42:38,420
then walking the "Heavenly Way"
will become an excuse of lynching others.

826
00:42:38,730 --> 00:42:40,810
I wonder how many members there are
in the Heavenly Way Society.

827
00:42:40,810 --> 00:42:43,360
If every one of them kills innocent people
like Wang Xin does,

828
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:45,560
won't that make the capital a living hell?

829
00:42:45,560 --> 00:42:48,000
I was going to tell Your Highnesses
about my findings.

830
00:42:48,000 --> 00:42:51,290
Based on the previously
calculated time of murders,

831
00:42:51,380 --> 00:42:53,010
I've roughly deduced

832
00:42:53,360 --> 00:42:55,810
the locations of the seven murders.

833
00:42:59,810 --> 00:43:01,940
How did you figure this out, Mr. Zhang?

834
00:43:08,640 --> 00:43:09,550
A compass?

835
00:43:10,830 --> 00:43:11,620
Exactly.

836
00:43:12,070 --> 00:43:13,680
Your Highnesses, do you know

837
00:43:13,710 --> 00:43:15,310
how the stars move in the sky?

838
00:43:17,730 --> 00:43:20,440
In ancient times,
the 24 solar terms were determined

839
00:43:20,440 --> 00:43:22,560
based on the movement of stars,

